        "range": "Self.",
        "overview": {
          "base": "During a <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Core:Short_Rest\" title=\"Core:Short Rest\" target=\"_blank\">short rest</a>, you may scavenge materials and make 1 melee <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Category:Weapons\" title=\"Category:Weapons\" target=\"_blank\">weapon</a>. Only common <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Damage:Mundane\" title=\"Damage:Mundane\" target=\"_blank\">mundane</a> items can typically be made in this way, but the <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Core:GM\" title=\"Core:GM\" target=\"_blank\">GM</a> may specify if other options are available to you. These items exist for 8 hours before they are no longer functional.",
          "proficient": "You can instead make up to <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Core:Proficiency_Bonus\" title=\"Core:Proficiency Bonus\" target=\"_blank\">P</a> weapons.",
          "fluent": "You can instead make up to <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Core:Fluency_Bonus\" title=\"Core:Fluency Bonus\" target=\"_blank\">F</a> weapons."
